      "content": "thanks. u mentioned the \"long-term benefits\" of a healthier environment, but for a local shop owner just trying to keep the lights on, that feels kinda vague. can u be more specific about how those environmental benefits actually translate into anything tangible for a small business's bottom line? or is it mostly just an abstract thing?",
